<lb n="0022c18"/>陀部。又出一部。名蘇跋梨沙柯部。亦名柯尸
<lb n="0022c19"/>悲<note n="0022029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔方梨反〕－【明】</note><app n="0022029"><lem><note place="inline">方梨反</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>與部。次從薩婆阿私底婆拖部。又出
<lb n="0022c20"/>一部。名僧千蘭底<note place="inline"><note n="0022030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">張履反＝音止【明】</note><app n="0022030"><lem>張履反</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">音止</rdg></app></note>婆拖部。亦名修丹
